RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CCY_CODE CCY1, A.CCY_NAME C1NAME, B.CCY_CODE CCY2, B.CCY_NAME C2NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN_MASTER A, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN_MASTER B WHERE A.CCY_CODE <> B.CCY_CODE AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND A.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = B.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY AND B.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = ? ORDER BY CCY1

SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN_MASTER CM WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = ? AND CCY_CODE IN ((SELECT CCY1 FROM CYTBS_CCY_PAIR_MASTER WHERE CCY2 = ? AND MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = CM.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY UNION SELECT CCY2 FROM CYTBS_CCY_PAIR_MASTER WHERE CCY1 = ? AND MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = CM.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY) INTERSECT (SELECT CCY1 FROM CYTBS_CCY_PAIR_MASTER WHERE CCY2 = ? AND MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = CM.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY UNION SELECT CCY2 FROM CYTBS_CCY_PAIR_MASTER WHERE CCY1 = ? AND MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY = CM.MAINTENANCE_COUNTRY)) ORDER BY CCY_CODE
